sbl-desc: A [https://www.semantic-mediawiki.org Semantic MediaWiki] extension to build breadcrumb links from an attributive property filter
smw-pa-property-predefined-sbl-parentpag: "$1" is a predefined property that can describe a relationship between a parent and a child entity and is provided by the [https://www.semantic-mediawiki.org/wiki/Extension:Semantic_Breadcrumb_Links Semantic Breadcrumb Links] extension.
smw-pa-property-predefined-long-sbl-pare: By identifying the location of an entity relative to its parent it can be used to generate a navigational help in form of a breadcrumb trail.
sbl-admin-deprecation-notice-title-repla: The following section contains settings that were renamed or otherwise modified and it is recommended to forthwith update their name or format.
